.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-resource\-describe \- Describe the supported live Grafana resource kinds and selector patterns.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util resource describe [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Describe the supported live Grafana resource kinds and selector patterns.
.PP
Use this when you want to know how the generic read\-only resource surface is shaped before you pick resource list or resource get.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B optional positional KIND
limit the output to one supported resource kind such as dashboards, folders, datasources, alert\-rules, or orgs
.TP
.B \-\-output\-format
choose text, table, json, or yaml
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Describe the supported live Grafana resource kinds and selector patterns.
.EX
grafana-util resource describe
.EE
